---
title: Cranberry-Mustard Turkey and Brie Cheese Melts with Apple and Radish Salad
description: A sweet and savoury cranberry-mustard spread makes these ooey- gooey brie and turkey melts standout from the crowd. A light and refreshing salad of apple, radish, spring mix and white wine vinaigrette brings balance to this easy and delicious meal.
